#: internal/cli/helpers.go:304
msgid ""
"provider 'google' requires an API key or Gemini OAuth login\n"
"\n"
"Option 1: Store an API key:\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider google\n"
"\n"
"Option 2: Login with Google OAuth (free tier: 60 req/min):\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider gemini\n"
"\n"
"Option 3: Pass key directly:\n"
"  --api-key YOUR_KEY or export GOOGLE_API_KEY=YOUR_KEY\n"
"\n"
"Get an API key from: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey"
msgstr ""
"المزوّد 'google' يتطلب مفتاح API أو تسجيل دخول Gemini OAuth\n"
"\n"
"الخيار 1: احفظ مفتاح API:\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider google\n"
"\n"
"الخيار 2: سجّل الدخول عبر Google OAuth (الطبقة المجانية: 60 طلب/دقيقة):\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider gemini\n"
"\n"
"الخيار 3: مرّر المفتاح مباشرة:\n"
"  --api-key YOUR_KEY or export GOOGLE_API_KEY=YOUR_KEY\n"
"\n"
"احصل على مفتاح API من: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey"

#: internal/cli/helpers.go:316
msgid ""
"provider 'gemini' requires Google OAuth login\n"
"\n"
"Login with your Google account:\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider gemini\n"
"\n"
"This uses Gemini Code Assist (free tier: 60 req/min).\n"
"For API key access, use --provider google instead."
msgstr ""
"المزوّد 'gemini' يتطلب تسجيل دخول Google OAuth\n"
"\n"
"سجّل الدخول باستخدام حساب Google الخاص بك:\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider gemini\n"
"\n"
"هذا يستخدم Gemini Code Assist (الطبقة المجانية: 60 طلب/دقيقة).\n"
"للوصول عبر مفتاح API، استخدم --provider google بدلاً من ذلك."

#: internal/cli/helpers.go:325
msgid ""
"provider 'groq' requires an API key\n"
"\n"
"Option 1: Store your API key:\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider groq\n"
"\n"
"Option 2: Pass key directly:\n"
"  --api-key YOUR_KEY or export GROQ_API_KEY=YOUR_KEY\n"
"\n"
"Get a free API key from: https://console.groq.com/keys"
msgstr ""
